parameters.name: X
parameters.description: Cartesian coords points towards the vernal equinox.

parameters.name: Y
parameters.description:
Cartesian coords points perpendicular to the 
                        ecliptic plane, positive towards the north ecliptic pole.

parameters.name: Vx
parameters.description:
Velocity of s/c (km, km/sec).
                     Represents the spacecraft's velocity along the x-axis, 
                     which points towards the Vernal Equinox.

parameters.name: Vy
parameters.description:
Velocity of s/c (km, km/sec).
                     Spacecraft's velocity along the y-axis, which lies 
                     in the ecliptic plane and is 90 degrees to the east 
                     (counter-clockwise) from the x-axis.

parameters.name: Vz
parameters.description:
Velocity of s/c (km, km/sec).
                     Spacecraft's velocity along the z-axis, which points 
                     towards the North Ecliptic Pole, perpendicular to the 
                     ecliptic plane.
